## Availability Blueprints
Blueprints
  # The main API availability SLO
  "api_availability":
    Requiring { env: String }
    Provides { vendor: "datadog" }

##  === Latency Blueprints ===
# These blueprints track latency
Blueprints
  "api_latency":
    Requiring { env: String }
    Provides { vendor: "datadog" }
